<h2 class="headline">Coronavirus Will Change the World Permanently. Here’s How.</h2>
<p class="dek">A crisis on this scale can reorder society in dramatic ways, for better or worse. Here are 34 big thinkers’ predictions for what’s to come.</p>
</div>
